  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This study is aimed to analyze the effects of aggressive and conventional lipid lowering
      therapy with Pravastatin on carotid intima-media thickness (IMT) in patients with
      hyperlipidemia and abnormal thickening of IMT.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
